<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#947721">{فَإِن تَابُواْ وَأَقَامُواْ الصَّلَاةَ وَآتَوُاْ الزَّكَاةَ فَخَلُّواْ سَبِيلَهُمْ}</span> ... <span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> ... ٢٠٩٢<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#947721">{فَإِن تَابُواْ وَأَقَامُواْ الصَّلَاةَ وَآتَوُاْ الزَّكَاةَ فَإِخْوَانُكُمْ فِي الدِّينِ}</span> ... <span style="color:#707070">[١١]</span> ... ٢٠٩٢<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#947721">{فَقَاتِلُواْ أَئِمَّةَ الْكُفْرِ}</span> ... <span style="color:#707070">[١٢]</span> ... ٤٩٨<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#947721">{وَالْمُؤَلَّفَةِ قُلُوبُهُمْ}</span> ... <span style="color:#707070">[٦٠]</span> ... ٢٩٩٦<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#947721">{أَبِاللهِ وَآيَاتِهِ وَرَسُولِهِ كُنتُمْ تَسْتَهْزِؤُون}</span> ... <span style="color:#707070">[٦٥]</span> ... ٢٧٢<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#947721">{أَبِاللهِ وَآيَاتِهِ وَرَسُولِهِ كُنتُمْ تَسْتَهْزِؤُون}</span> ... <span style="color:#707070">[٦٥]</span> ... ١٢٦٧<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#947721">{وَلَا تُصَلِّ عَلَى أَحَدٍ مِّنْهُم مَّاتَ أَبَدًا وَلَا تَقُمْ عَلَىَ قَبْرِهِ}</span> ... <span style="color:#707070">[٨٤]</span> ... ١١٧٠<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#947721">{إِنَّ اللهَ اشْتَرَى مِنَ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ أَنفُسَهُمْ وَأَمْوَالَهُم بِأَنَّ لَهُمُ الجَنَّةَ يُقَاتِلُونَ فِي سَبِيلِ اللهِ فَيَقْتُلُونَ وَيُقْتَلُونَ}</span> ... <span style="color:#707070">[١١١]</span> ... ١٤٦٢<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
